lower = np.array([0, 0, 0])
upper = np.array([100, 255, 255])
mask = cv2.inRange(hsv, lower, upper)

img_mask = cv2.bitwise_and(img, img, mask=mask)

cv2.waitKey(0)
cv2.destroyAllWindows()
